OL,3,CO'Dowd halts business rates process
OL,4,Cafter hospitality backlash
OL,6,FA proposed revaluation of business
OL,7,Frates has been stopped, Stormont's
OL,8,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd has said.
OL,10,FThe Reval 2026 process had led to a
OL,11,Fbacklash from many within the
OL,12,Fhospitality sector who had said they
OL,13,Fwere facing higher rates bills.
OL,15,FThe Minister said he wants local
OL,16,Fbusinesses to 'thrive' as they are
OL,17,F'the backbone of our communities'.
