OL,3,CO'Dowd halts business rates process
OL,4,Cafter hospitality backlash
OL,6,FSpeaking on Thursday, Mr O'Dowd said:
OL,7,F"I have listened carefully and I am
OL,8,Fvery aware of the concerns raised by
OL,9,Fbusinesses ` particularly hotels, pubs
OL,10,Fand other hospitality businesses.
OL,12,F"I remain in listening mode, I will
OL,13,Fnow consider the next steps.
OL,15,F"My focus remains on supporting our
OL,16,Fpublic services, our local businesses
OL,17,Fand growing our economy."
