OL,3,CO'Dowd halts business rates process
OL,4,Cafter hospitality backlash
OL,6,FLast week, Mr O'Dowd announced Reval
OL,7,F2026, as Land and Property Services
OL,8,F(LPS) released a draft list of
OL,9,Frevaluations for commercial properties.
OL,11,FProperties that had seen above average
OL,12,Fincreases in their value faced an
OL,13,Foverall rating liability increase,
OL,14,Fresulting in a higher rates bill.
OL,16,FHospitality Ulster, which had
OL,17,Fdescribed the original proposals as
OL,18,F"unacceptable", welcomed the latest
OL,19,Fannouncement by the minister.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@NO]
