OL,3,CO'Dowd halts business rates process
OL,4,Cafter hospitality backlash
OL,6,FChief executive Colin Neill said: "At
OL,7,Fa time when hurt and anxiety were at
OL,8,Fall-time highs in the sector, it is a
OL,9,Frelief that the minister has listened
OL,10,Fto the people who are both a
OL,11,Fcornerstone of our economy and who
OL,12,Fprovide an invaluable service to our
OL,13,Fsociety.
OL,15,F"This demonstrates the value of having
OL,16,Flocally elected politicians that can
OL,17,Fintervene.
OL,26,@nD@cOUwD@AOU
