OL,3,CO'Dowd halts business rates process
OL,4,Cafter hospitality backlash
OL,6,F"Hospitality's opposition to Reval
OL,7,F2026 has never been based on an
OL,8,Funwillingness to contribute our fair
OL,9,Fshare to rates revenue, but about
OL,10,Fcommunicating that what was proposed
OL,11,Fwas not fair and would have been the
OL,12,Fdeath knell for our industry.
OL,14,F"We now look forward to working with
OL,15,Fthe minister to come to a solution
OL,16,Fthat allows the sector to pay its fair
OL,17,Fshare and develop at the same time,
OL,18,Fallowing the sector to contribute
OL,19,Fpositively to the growth of the
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland economy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
