OL,3,CO'Dowd halts business rates process
OL,4,Cafter hospitality backlash
OL,6,F"We also need clarity on whether the
OL,7,Fminister received a briefing from Land
OL,8,F& Property Services in advance of
OL,9,Ftheir findings on the Reval 2026
OL,10,Fexercise.
OL,12,F"If so, why did he not foresee how
OL,13,Fdamaging this would be to the
OL,14,Fcornerstone of hospitality in Northern
OL,15,FIreland?"
OL,17,FShe added: "I hold this minister
OL,18,Fwholly responsible for the widespread
OL,19,Falarm he has caused across the
OL,20,Findustry.
